result.execSummary:
The defendant Stevie J Money Jr was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Stevie J Money Jr is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Stevie J Money Jr was found guilty of Intimidate Victim/Dissuade Reporting [Modifiers: Domestic Abuse, Domestic Abuse Repeater], an unclassified felony, Wisconsin Statutes 940.44(1).
  • Stevie J Money Jr was found guilty of Disorderly Conduct [Modifiers: Domestic Abuse], a class B misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 947.01(1).

Notice to employers: It may be a violation of state law to discriminate against a job applicant because of an arrest or conviction record.
